<olink targetdoc="refman" targetptr="pkg-7"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>pkg</refentrytitle><manvolnum>7</manvolnum></citerefentry></olink> man page for more information about <literal>tag-name</literal> and
<replaceable>pattern</replaceable>.</para>
